  <brief_title>The Effects of Oscillating-Rotating Electric Toothbrushes on Plaque and Gingival Health</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Oscillating-Rotating Electric Toothbrushes on Plaque and Gingival Health: A Meta-Analysis</official_title>
