  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this analysis was to compare the effects of oscillating-rotating (O-R),
      side-to-side (sonic), and manual toothbrushes on plaque and gingival health after multiple
      uses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
